POJO

Class Poll

  • java.lang.Object
    • POJO.Poll

  • public class Poll
extends java.lang.Object
    POJO representing a poll. It is made of :
    • an id
    • the question of the poll
    • an ArrayList containing the answers of the poll
    • The creator of the poll
    Author:
    Max Cabourg
